    "These instructions are versatile, serving both as guidance for finetuning LLMs and as a benchmark for evaluating the models' proficiency in executing API-related instructions.",
    "• ToolBench (Xu et al, 2023f).",
    "The ToolBench dataset encompasses 795 instructions in English, designed to evaluate the proficiency of LLMs in manipulating various tools.",
    "The dataset is compiled from five pre-existing datasets and three recently acquired datasets.",
    "Evaluation tasks span diverse domains, including open weather, the cat API, home search, trip booking, Google Sheets, virtual home, webshop, and tabletop."
